Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.59,0:00:03.44,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,Next up is a rookie \Nmaking his first appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.69,0:00:06.55,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,Car 86, driven by a \Nchallenger from England.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.55,0:00:09.07,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,Katagiri Kanata, 19 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.84,0:00:11.07,Italics,Seven,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:18.08,Italics,Seven,0000,0000,0000,,Are you kidding me? Is that really him?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.94,0:00:25.09,Italics,Seven,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here, Kanata?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.69,0:00:30.42,Italics,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,Is it me or did she just look\Nreally surprised for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:30.42,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,Six. Five. Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.42,0:00:32.91,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,Three. Two. One.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.32,0:00:38.42,Italics,Seven,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.96,0:01:10.75,Default,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,)\blur5\t(0,310,\blur0.3)\fax-0.2\bord0\fnImpact\shad0\fs90\b1\c&HFFFFFF&\t(560,561,\c&H6000E6&)\t(580,1000,\c&H0100D1&)\pos(320,345)}MF Ghost
